(1429, 2, 'mfn-page-items-seo', 'Heading\n\n<h3>FOLLOWS DETAILS OF NEXT SYMPOSIUM 2017</h3>\r\n[divider height="25"]\r\n<h5>4 th SYMPOSIUM in BANGKOK - THAILAND</h5>\r\n<h4>From september 22 th up to september 24 th , 2017 </h4>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n20px\n\n120px 0 0\n\nSep\n\n<div style="background: url(http://www.lcn.agenciaondaforte.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_sep.png) repeat-x; height: 3px;"></div>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n20px\n\nButton\n\n[button title="MORE INFO" link="/lcna-conferences/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="theme" font_color="" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n15px 0 0\n\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/symposium-red.png" alt=""/>\n\n/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/symposium-black.png\n\n<a href="#">#</a>\n\nGallery Conferences\n\n<h1 style="color:#fff;">4th SYMPOSIUM in IGUASSU FALLS – BRAZIL</h1>\r\n<h6 style="color:#fff;">From September 19 Th Up To September 23 Th , 2015 </h6>\r\n[button title="VIEW PHOTO GALLERY" link="/2016-conference/" target="" icon="icon-camera" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n40px 0 0 0\n\n<h1 style="color:#fff;">PAST CONFERENCES</h1>\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2016" link="/2016-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2015" link="/2015-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2014" link="/2014-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2013" link="/2013-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2012" link="/2012-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2011" link="/2011-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/conference-home.jpg" alt=""/>\n\ncenter\n\n50\n\nConference\n\n<h3 style="color:#fff;">CONFERENCE</h3>\r\n<p style="color:#fff;">Every single year LCN promotes an annual conference, where the members have the opportunity to meet each other in only one business trip. In order to benefit the partners from all continents, LCN will organise its conferences in a different country and continent a year. In addition to that, the conference period will be always the same, during the first semester of the year. <br><br>\r\nIn this way, everybody is able to guarantee his participation in advance. <br><br>\r\nAs one of the main rules, it will not be allowed to be absent from more than two consecutive conferences. You may be right that the conferences represent more an investment than a real cost.</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n50px 0 30px 0\n\nProduct\n\n[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/statute.jpg" border="0"]\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<div style="padding: 20px 6%; background: url(/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_sep2.png) repeat-y right top">\r\n<h4>Statute</h4>\r\n<p>Know what is the statute that governs all activity LCN</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px;"><i class="icon-doc-text themecolor"></i> <a href="/lcna-statute/">Learn More</a></p>\r\n</div>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 3% 0 0\n\nProduct\n\n[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/judges.jpg" border="0"]\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<div style="padding: 20px 6%; background: url(/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_sep2.png) repeat-y right top">\r\n<h4>Judges Commisioners</h4>\r\n<p>The LCN Judge Commisioners has been established in order to assist our members in any problem with another company.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px;"><i class="icon-doc-text themecolor"></i> <a href="/lcna-judges/">Learn More</a></p>\r\n</div>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 3% 0 0\n\nProduct\n\n[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/education.jpg" border="0"]\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<div style="padding: 20px 6%; background: url(/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_sep2.png) repeat-y right top">\r\n<h4>District Manager</h4>\r\n<p>The LCN district managers are in charge for introducing new and reliable companies to the Association.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px;"><i class="icon-doc-text themecolor"></i> <a href="/lcna-district/">Learn More</a></p>\r\n</div>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 3% 0 0\n\nProduct\n\n[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/export.jpg" border="0"]\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<div style="padding: 20px 6%;">\r\n<h4>L3P Payment Protection Program</h4>\r\n<p>L3P is a new Lcn program created in order to offer to Lcn members a protection service against bad payer agents.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px;"><i class="icon-doc-text themecolor"></i> <a href="/lcna-w3p/">Learn More</a></p>\r\n</div>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 3% 0 0\n\nHeading\n\n<h2 style="color: #fff; margin: 0 5%;">MEMBERS</h2>\r\n[divider height="30"]\r\n<div style="background: url(/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_sep3.png) repeat-x; height: 3px; margin: 0 25%;"></div>\r\n<p style="">LCNA Association has over 100 members worldwide located on different continents. This information is available to members only.</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nHeading\n\n<h3 style="color: #fff; margin: 0 5%;">IF YOU ARE A MEMBER, PLESE LOGIN IN MEMBER AREA</h3>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nLogin Member Area\n\n<a href="/members-list/">/members-list/</a>\n\ncenter\n\nicon-lock\n\nleft\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style="color: #032c27; letter-spacing: 5px">ANNUAL FEE</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_heading_icon2.png" border="0"]</p>\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<p><b>LCN ANNUAL MEMBERSHIP FEE</b><br>\r\nDear partner, in order to serve you and your company with quality, efficiency and competence, LCN charges an annuity from its members. The annuity is:<br>\r\n<b>USD 650,00</b> - for head offices. <br>\r\n<b>USD 50,00</b> - for branch offices located in the same country of the head office.<br><br>\r\nIn LCN is allowed until three partners in the same country. There are exceptions for Brazil, China, India, The United States because these are big countries and United Arab Emirates due the big volume of cargo.<br><br>\r\nWe are sure that this is more an investment than a cost.<br>\r\nJoin us and you will not regret it!</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style="color: #032c27; letter-spacing: 5px">FIDELITY PROGRAM</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_heading_icon2.png" border="0"]</p>\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<p>The<b> fidelity program</b> is a way to become our group stronger and benefit you at the same time. By indicating at least three new members, you will have your next annual fee costless and if you bring 5 new members you will receive the next annual conference free of charge.<br><br>\r\nFor the time being, LCN counts on more than 100 partners, representing almost 80 countries of the whole world, and we do intend to increase this number.<br><br>\r\nSome of our partners have already been indicating new agents to us and they will certainly receive the benefits for their support. <br><br>\r\nOur major goal as an international freight forwarder association is to reach the whole world, keeping together the companies as one unique team.<br><br>\r\nThe outcomes of your participation at the Fidelity Program will be favourable to all.<br><br>\r\nWe do count on you,</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style="color: #032c27; letter-spacing: 5px">SALES LEADS PROGRAM</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_heading_icon2.png" border="0"]</p>\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<p><b>To increase more business between the members, all members must attendance this programm.</b><br><br>\r\nEach month each member must send to us your report of how many sales leads you generated and to whom.<br><br>\r\nWe will analize which members are working for obtain more benefits w/ another members.</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<h3 style="color:#fff;">JOIN US/APLICATION FORM</h3>\r\n[divider height="25"]\r\n<p style="color:#fff;">Dear partner, thanks a lot for your interest in our association, we are sure that our group may strengthen even more your business. In order to join us, please, you have to take the following steps<br><br>\r\n1. Fill up the application form (available at application form link) and send it to us, so that we may know more about your company:<br>\r\n2. After sending the form, we from LCN head office will contact you for any doubt;<br> \r\n3. The third step is the payment of the LCN annual membership fee. The annuity lasts twelve months, which means that if you join us in December of a year, then, you will have to pay the fee again only in next December; <br>\r\n4. After the payment of the annuity, LCN will prepare a circular message and introduce your good company to every partners. <br>\r\n5. You will also receive a password and an username for accessing our web site with no restrictions.<br><br>\r\nWe do count on you,<br><br>\r\nFor any doubt, feel free to contact us anytime,</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n30px\n\n50px 0 0\n\ndefault\n\nGo To Aplication Form\n\n<a href="/aplication/">/aplication/</a>\n\ncenter\n\nicon-window\n\nleft\n\n3\n\nHeading\n\n<h3 style="color: #fff; margin: 0 5%;">THE BLACK LIST</h3>\r\n<p style="color: #fff; margin: 0 5%;">We have a black list containing the name of some agents worldwide.</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nView The Black List\n\n<a href="/black-list/">/black-list/</a>\n\ncenter\n\nicon-cancel-circled\n\nleft\n\n2\n\n'),
