(1689, 345, 'mfn-page-items-seo', 'Heading\n\n<h3>Avani Riverside Bangkok Hotel</h3>\r\n<p>257 Charoennakom Road, Samrae, Thonburi, Bangkok 10600 – Thailand</p>\r\n[divider height="25"]\r\n<h5>DEAR PARTNERS<br>\r\nFOLLOWS DETAILS OF NEXT SYMPOSIUM 2017</h5>\r\n[divider height="25"]\r\n<h5>DEAR MEMBERSHIPS</h5>\r\n<p>We have the pleasure to announced the details for next meeting as follows</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n20px\n\n10px 0 0\n\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hotel-01.jpg" alt=""/>\n\nHeading\n\n<h3>INCLUDED BELOW DETAILS</h3>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> Airport transfer / airport / hotel / airport <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> registration at Breeze – 10 fllor <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> city tour = 13 hs on 09.22 at Pier of the hotel <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> welcome cocktail = 19 hs up to 21 hs at Atitude bar – special clothes are required - color white <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> 2 Coffee Breaks per day on sept 23 and 24 <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> 2 Lunches ( sept 23 and 24), <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> 1 gala dinner (sept 24 ) <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> Conference Room , w/ internet included.<br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> Conference Material are included.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h3>NOT ARE INCLUDED:</h3>\r\n<h5>BY YOUR OWN ACCOUNT AND CHOICE</h5><br><br>\r\n\r\n<i class="icon-cancel-circled"></i> Airport transfer <br>\r\n<i class="icon-cancel-circled"></i> Accommodation, IF YOU WANT TO STAY AT SAME HOTEL , FOLLOWS THE PRICES AND PAYMENT AND RESERVATIONS MUST BE DONE DIRECTLY WITH HOTEL <br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>1 OPTION Avani River View Room</b><br>\r\nSingle room = baht 3.800 + 17% taxies <br>\r\nDouble room = baht 4.300 + 17 % taxies <br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>2 OPTION Junior River View Room</b><br>\r\nSingle room = baht 6.300 + 17% taxies <br>\r\nDouble room = baht 6.800 + 17 % taxies <br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>INCLUDED AT BOOKING ROOMS:</b><br>\r\n- International buffet breakfast <br>\r\n- Internet <br>\r\n- Coffee and tea facilities <br>\r\n- Bottled drinking water <br>\r\n- Fitness center.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h3>P.S. – SOME CONSIDERATIONS</h3>\r\n<b>WE WILL PROVIDE A LINK FOR ALL MEMBERS DO YOUR OWN BOOKING RESERVATION DIRECTLY WITH HOTEL</b><br>\r\n• If the prices increased, be informed that we do not have any responsibility , will depends of space available <br>\r\n• The rooms not support 3 people at same room. <br>\r\n• Bookings must be done up to 09.15 to guarantee space at same hotel <br><br>\r\n\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> Check in 15 hs <br>\r\n<i class="icon-check"></i> Check out 12 hs <br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Lunch for 09. 22 and dinner for 09. 22 & 23 – for your account</b>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n20px\n\n10px 0 0\n\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hotel-04.jpg" alt=""/>\n\nHeading\n\n<h3>The Hotel Offer:</h3>\r\n Restaurant <br>\r\n Bars <br>\r\n Swimming Pool <br>\r\n Room service <br>\r\n Fitness Center <br>\r\n SPA & Beauty Salon and Barber shop & Massage <br>\r\n Sauna <br>\r\n Business center <br>\r\n boutique<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h3>SPECIAL CONSIDERATIONS - MANDATORY</h3>\r\n<b>1 –</b> Sport clothes during the Conference period;<br>\r\n<b>2 -</b> Bring a typical gift of your country PER PERSON NOT PER COMPANY for a lottery;<br>\r\n<b>3 -</b> Small flag of your country;<br>\r\n<b>4 -</b> Your company profile and business card for distribution to another members.\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n20px\n\n10px 0 0\n\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hotel-03.jpg" alt=""/>\n\nHeading\n\n<h3>CANCELLATION POLICY</h3>\r\n<p>1 - Extremely important: For those who confirm the participation, Lcn & Wcna. For those who cancel the participation after payment,, not be possible to reimburse the values already paid.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>AGENDA</h3>\r\n<p>PLEASE BE INFORMED THAT THE AGENDA OF THE 5th SYMPOSIUM AS FOLLOWS:<br><br>\r\n<b>1ST DAY –</b> september 22 th – CITY TOUR - 1 PM AT pier of the hotel , backing 5 PM <br>\r\n7:00 Pm UP TO 9:00 pm - WELLCOME COKTAIL AT ATITUDE BAR , SPECIAL WHITE CLOTHES ARE REQUIRED<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>2ND AND 3 RD DAY –</b> september 23 th and 24<br>\r\nCONFERENCE AT MAIN MEETING ROOM – LUNNAR ROOM ( Sport Clothes ) - 10 FLOOR<br>\r\nFROM 8:30 AM UP TO 6:00 PM<br><br>\r\n\r\n09.24 - 8:30 pm – GALA DINNER at Galaxy - 11 floor<br> \r\nTYPICAL THAI SHOW – CABARET<br>\r\nCERTIFICATES + LOTERY AFTER SHOW<br><br>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n20px\n\n10px 0 0\n\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/hotel-02.jpg" alt=""/>\n\nHeading\n\n[member]\r\n<div style="text-align:left;"><h3>RESERVATIONS - Conference Fee</h3>\r\n<b>1 ST DEAD LINE TILL</b> : JUNE 30, 2017	USD 849,00 PER PERSON<br>\r\n<b>2 ND DEAD LINE TILL</b> : JULY 31, 2017	USD 949,00 PER PERSON<br>\r\n<b>3 RD DEAD LINE TILL</b> : AUGUST 31, 2017	USD 1049,00 PER PERSON<br>\r\n<b>Payments must be done as soon as you require the invoice to us : </b></div>\r\n<h4>PLEASE COMPLETE YOUR CONFERENCE REGISTRATION HERE</h4>\r\n[contact-form-7 id="930" title="Conference"]\r\n<p>And send your confirmation to Edson: <a href="mailto:edson@lcnassociation.com">edson@lcnassociation.com</a> or <a href="mailto:edson@lcnassociation.com">edson@lcnassociation.com</a><br>\r\nWe need to know: Airline, flight number, date of arrival and departure from your side.</p>\r\n[/member]\r\n<div style="text-align:left;"><h3>FINAL CONSIDERATIONS</h3>\r\nIS 100% FORBIDEN BRING ANY KIND OF BEVERAGE AND FOOD TO THE HOTEL FM OUTSIDE, A HIGH PENALTY WILL BE APPLYED AT YR ROOM.<br>\r\nWCNA & LCN NOT RECEIVED ANY KIND OF SUPPORT LIKE SPONSORS.<br>\r\nWe are sure that this will be a great event for the development of your business. We count on your participation in order to become our group even stronger.<br>\r\nPlease, provide your payment as soon as possible in order to guarantee your reservation.<br>\r\nMORE DETAILS OF CONFERENCE CAME SOON,......<br><br>\r\n\r\nREMEMBER ..........WHO IS NOT THERE, USUALLY NOT WILL BE REMEMBERED BY ANOTHER MEMBERS ...........<br>\r\nFor any doubt, please, do not hesitate to contact me anytime.<br>\r\nBest Regards<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>EDSON B. ZAPPAROLI</b></div>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0px\n\nGallery Conferences\n\n<h1 style="color:#fff;">PASTE CONFERENCES</h1>\r\n[button title="VIEW PHOTO GALLERY" link="/2016-conference/" target="" icon="icon-camera" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n40px 0 0 0\n\n<h1 style="color:#fff;">PAST CONFERENCES</h1>\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2016" link="/2016-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2015" link="/2015-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2014" link="/2014-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2013" link="/2013-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2012" link="/2012-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\r\n[button title="CONFERENCE 2011" link="/2011-conference/" target="" icon="" icon_position="" color="#242b33" font_color="#fff" size="2" full_width="" class="" download="" onclick=""]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n'),
