ter-spacing: 5px">ANNUAL FEE</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_heading_icon2.png" border="0"]</p>\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<p><b>LCN ANNUAL MEMBERSHIP FEE</b><br>\r\nDear partner, in order to serve you and your company with quality, efficiency and competence, LCN charges an annuity from its members. The annuity is:<br>\r\n<b>USD 650,00</b> - for head offices. <br>\r\n<b>USD 50,00</b> - for branch offices located in the same country of the head office.<br><br>\r\nIn LCN is allowed until three partners in the same country. There are exceptions for Brazil, China, India, The United States because these are big countries and United Arab Emirates due the big volume of cargo.<br><br>\r\nWe are sure that this is more an investment than a cost.<br>\r\nJoin us and you will not regret it!</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style="color: #032c27; letter-spacing: 5px">FIDELITY PROGRAM</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_heading_icon2.png" border="0"]</p>\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<p>The<b> fidelity program</b> is a way to become our group stronger and benefit you at the same time. By indicating at least three new members, you will have your next annual fee costless and if you bring 5 new members you will receive the next annual conference free of charge.<br><br>\r\nFor the time being, LCN counts on more than 100 partners, representing almost 80 countries of the whole world, and we do intend to increase this number.<br><br>\r\nSome of our partners have already been indicating new agents to us and they will certainly receive the benefits for their support. <br><br>\r\nOur major goal as an international freight forwarder association is to reach the whole world, keeping together the companies as one unique team.<br><br>\r\nThe outcomes of your participation at the Fidelity Program will be favourable to all.<br><br>\r\nWe do count on you,</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nDesc\n\n<h4 style="color: #032c27; letter-spacing: 5px">SALES LEADS PROGRAM</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align:center;">[image src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/home_agro_heading_icon2.png" border="0"]</p>\r\n[divider height="20"]\r\n<p><b>To increase more business between the members, all members must attendance this programm.</b><br><br>\r\nEach month each member must send to us your report of how many sales leads you generated and to whom.<br><br>\r\nWe will analize which members are working for obtain more benefits w/ another members.</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n'),
